<item>
 <title>Believe Me</title>
 <link>http://vse.la/yulia-savicheva/believe-me</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Believe me, I just don’t care&lt;br /&gt;
If you look away or stare,&lt;br /&gt;
If you choose to go or stay&lt;br /&gt;
Don’t believe me, I pray!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In my head — every day, everywhere — oh, no&lt;br /&gt;
You and I can talk, and I sound colder.&lt;br /&gt;
In my heart, though I say I don’t care,&lt;br /&gt;
I just cry and cry on your big shoulder.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[Chorus:]&lt;br /&gt;
Believe me, I just don’t care&lt;br /&gt;
If you look away or stare,&lt;br /&gt;
If you choose to go or stay&lt;br /&gt;
Don’t believe me, I pray!&lt;br /&gt;
Believe me, I just don’t care&lt;br /&gt;
If you look away or stare,&lt;br /&gt;
If you choose to go or stay&lt;br /&gt;
Don’t believe me, I pray!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Far away, like the man in the Moon, (my dear!)&lt;br /&gt;
You just wave to me, you are always lying.&lt;br /&gt;
Every face, every voice, every tune&lt;br /&gt;
Brings you back to me, and I start crying!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Chorus)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Believe me, I just don’t care...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
